{"tid":2281701,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"城大女生急性肝衰竭陷昏迷　急需 A 或 O 型血肝移植","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T15:50:11.000Z","uid":219732,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6550fa3d9741f7d4dd362eb4e9ff99514baccc42","tid":2281701,"uid":219732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"20 歲城市大學化學系學生、保良局李城璧中學校友鄭如妍本月初患上急性肝衰竭，現正留醫瑪麗醫院深切治療部，急需換肝續命。其親友今（ 11 日）發文呼籲有心人士捐肝，好友邱小姐向《立場新聞》透露，如妍上月起持續發燒未退，服藥治療後出現急性肝衰竭，其後變得神智不清，更陷入昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n若本周仍沒有合適人士捐肝，如妍或未能渡過今個周末；邱小姐形容如妍為人活潑、孝順，一直希望盡快大學畢業，賺錢供養母親。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44TDSqg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44TDSqg.png&h=6ba0b8b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望有適合既肝救返鄭同學"},{"pid":"a1dfc8dce3d52066e5798aae066079fa54b8e8e4","tid":2281701,"uid":3063,"like":11,"dislike":38,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"靚女有特權？"},{"pid":"3be81e8a83faea98d3ac53a101b7d55153e31352","tid":2281701,"uid":15057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:35:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"322edfa98e92e0c2869be3618bd833700a5da41c","tid":2281701,"uid":307249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:36:59.000Z","msg":"睇嚟案件要重演 lm睇大愛撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n20歲女急需換肝 希望O+有心人可以幫忙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573429</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d2c2319ea740a0e74502d4e2af7493a13ef9592f","tid":2281701,"uid":191150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"希望搵到合適肝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333e21427f7b66cd4b2ace164a8551a274378d55","tid":2281701,"uid":230714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7d6c024bbff767ad43dfdea9fc2b00a6112b5ba